wp_pdf
======

WordPress / asciidoc / a2x / docbook / latex / pdf

- setup site in Linode VPS: +
  http://library.linode.com/hosting-website#sph_configuring-name-based-virtual-hosts
- create a database on Linode VPS: +
  http://library.linode.com/hosting-website#sph_creating-a-database
- install Wordpress: +
  http://library.linode.com/web-applications/cms-guides/wordpress
- add the following to wp-config.php

  ```
  // forces the filesystem method: "direct", "ssh", "ftpext", or "ftpsockets"
  define('FS_METHOD', 'direct');
  // absolute path to root installation directory
  define('FTP_BASE', '/home/patrick/public/star.the-huck.com/public/');
  // absolute path to "wp-content" directory
  define('FTP_CONTENT_DIR', '/home/patrick/public/star.the-huck.com/public/wp-content/');
  // absolute path to "wp-plugins" directory
  define('FTP_PLUGIN_DIR ', '/home/patrick/public/star.the-huck.com/public/wp-content/plugins/');
  // absolute path to your SSH public key
  define('FTP_PUBKEY', '/home/patrick/.ssh/id_rsa_wp-star.pub');
  // absolute path to your SSH private key
  define('FTP_PRIVKEY', '/home/patrick/.ssh/id_rsa_wp-star');
  // either your FTP or SSH username
  define('FTP_USER', 'patrick');
  // password for FTP_USER username
  //define('FTP_PASS', 'password');
  // hostname:port combo for your SSH/FTP server
  define('FTP_HOST', 'the-huck.com');
  ```

- sudo chown -R www-data:www-data public/
- list of plugins:
  - Options Framework
  - Disable Comments
  - CMS Page Order
  - Multi-level Navigation Plugin
  - WP Google Fonts
  - WP PHP widget
- use asciidoc userguide.txt as example case

